001|# React + TypeScript + Vite
002|
003|This template provides a minimal setup to get React working in Vite with HMR and some ESLint rules.
004|
005|Currently, two official plugins are available:
006|
007|- [@vitejs/plugin-react](https://github.com/vitejs/vite-plugin-react/blob/main/packages/plugin-react/README.md) uses [Babel](https://babeljs.io/) for Fast Refresh
008|- [@vitejs/plugin-react-swc](https://github.com/vitejs/vite-plugin-react-swc) uses [SWC](https://swc.rs/) for Fast Refresh
009|
010|All shadcn/ui components have been downloaded under `@/components/ui`.
